    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "\"accept it and move on\"... but what if moving on just means carrying this weight forever? it feels so heavy. like, if i'm just stuck being this broken version of myself, does it even matter if i keep pushing through? it feels more like i'm just prolonging the inevitable.",
